	<li>
		<i><a name="cygwin"></a>
			Some tests are disabled due to incomplete Cygwin support for handling signals in threads.
		</i>
	</li>
	<li>
		<i><a name="note_fork"></a>
			Many important features are missing from this port due to lack of POSIX compatibility
